msgstr "வளங்கள்"

#. Resource
#: ../content/55_activity_36.md:block 20 (unordered list)
#, md-text
msgid ""
"[4 innovations we owe to open "
"source](https://www.techrepublic.com/article/4-innovations-we-owe-to-open-"
"source/)."
msgstr ""
"[4 innovations we owe பெறுநர் திற "
